  <summary date="2017-06-23T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Student Loan Interest Deduction Act of 2017

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) increase the maximum tax deduction for interest paid on any qualified education loan to $5,000 ($10,000 for married couples filing a joint tax return), and (2) repeal the limitation on such deduction based upon modified adjusted gross income.</summary>
